{"tid":381977,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【股神嫌貴了】畢菲特：股票吸引力下降 搵平股更困難","createTime":"2017-08-31T11:03:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T11:03:36.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c80fc2073a7463792196c06bad3d7c0c54450478","tid":381977,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T11:03:36.000Z","msg":"【新增影片】<br />\n<br />\n股神畢菲特表示，過去幾年市場上升，要尋找便宜股票顯得更困難，但相比債券，他仍更願意選擇股票。他謂：「股票的吸引力在逐步下降&hellip;但與債券相比，它們仍然非常有吸引力。」<br />\n<br />\n當被問及為什麼畢菲特旗下的巴郡現金越積越多時，他告訴《彭博》：「這只是在告訴我們，股票與大部分時間相比都已經不再便宜。」畢菲特並表示，在2008年金融危機之後購買股票就像是「在桶裡射魚」。<br />\n<br />\n畢菲特亦接受CNBC訪問，透露從未沽售過蘋果股票，但拒絕透露是否正在增持該股。<br />\n<br />\n談及美國經濟，畢菲特指目前並不似處於一個經濟增長達3%的美國，反而似是增幅2%左右，但相信正在加速。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170831/large/1504150285_85a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170831%2Flarge%2F1504150285_85a5.jpg&h=54869258&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57151093&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170831\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57151093%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170831&d=xkDhTH0%2BgIIGeBhui0X5BcP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=369193cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57151093%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170831&h=ba5f3080\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57151093&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170831</a>"}]}